    <p>Our platform offers two convenient settings: "For Sale" and "For Rent," allowing you to explore a wide range of properties on the market. Here's how you can customize your search:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Price Range:</strong> Set your budget with minimum and maximum price filters.</li>
        <li><strong>Location:</strong> Narrow down your search by selecting your desired state and city.</li>
        <li><strong>House Type:</strong> Select from various property types, including houses, condos, townhouses, multihome, lot/land, and manufactured homes, with our convenient checkboxes.</li>
        <li><strong>Bedrooms & Bathrooms:</strong> Find the ideal home by specifying the minimum and maximum number of bedrooms and bathrooms.</li>
        <li><strong>Living Size:</strong> Choose the living space that suits your family's needs with our minimum and maximum living size filters.</li>
        <li><strong>Lot Size:</strong> Whether you're looking for a spacious yard or a cozy lot, our lot size filters have you covered.</li>
